Shalane McCall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shalane_McCall 0 Shalane McCall (born September 16, 1972) is a former American child actress and model, best known for appearing for five seasons (1983–1988) on the hit CBS prime time soap opera Dallas playing Charlotte "Charlie" Wade, the daughter of Jenna Wade (Priscilla Presley).
